{"tid":1124653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得香港人係全世界最難服侍","createTime":"2019-04-25T07:16:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T00:23:32.000Z","uid":31637,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4eddda7cafb924a4996169f009e763af5ecbae01","tid":1124653,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:16:19.000Z","msg":"又唔想太高文明<br />\n又唔比太低文明<br />\n<br />\n要中中間間, 恰到好處<br />\n<br />\n以獨裁管治香港為例, 香港人只愛同接受團派既佛系獨裁, 極反對習近平果隻咩都要插手,咩都要管既FUCK系獨裁<br />\n<br />\n以西方民主國家為例, 香港人極反對好似耶穌咁,以割肉方式或以大愛去感化同包容所有人既民主國家, 反而鐘意識得禮尚往來或以牙還牙, 萬倍奉還既民主國家<br />\n<br />\n咁你話香港人係唔係全世界最撚難服侍"},{"pid":"9d1eb63e00eb5c60ea592c50421ae214056999c1","tid":1124653,"uid":48500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:26:53.000Z","msg":"香港人係要外國既工時日本既配套外國既居住環境,取各國之長先係生活,否則都係做狗,最好就政府派樓啦,太舊又唔好太cheap"},{"pid":"5f7c0e79067f041cf39665be86c37d64561732a8","tid":1124653,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:13:43.000Z","msg":"香港人係想好似北歐社會咁但又唔想大愛包容,咁又點成為北歐模式<br />\n其實冇話要你大愛哂所有人,淨係愛自己人都唔得啦"},{"pid":"fcb838f3d870b54228375c853ce265d5a64c2bc2","tid":1124653,"uid":53628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T22:59:55.000Z","msg":"仲有新加坡同印度"},{"pid":"1147e761264b7fcd87f6cf43df00febafb20f8e4","tid":1124653,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T00:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fcd42e1b8f6ffcfe5d6ed0d797dfa3f0ce50f4c","tid":1124653,"uid":76135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T00:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/26/082256_a5dfec5421036f506663ffaf06299c1c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F26%2F082256_a5dfec5421036f506663ffaf06299c1c.jpeg&h=b8c65539&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}